---
title: Cajun Fried Chicken with sweet potato mash and zesty shredded salad
description: Earthy herbs and smoky spices are hallmarks of Cajun cuisine. It just so happens that both pair particularly well with crispy breaded fried chicken as you'll see in this simple and super delicious recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF200720_R08_W37_SE_C12343757-2_KB_main_high-d80183e3.jpg
